Class LongestCommonSubsequence<T extends Diffable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.pl.util.diff.lcs.LongestCommonSubsequence<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ComplexLCS, LineBasedLCS, ValueLCS

    public abstract class LongestCommonSubsequence<T extends Diffable<T>>
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to compute the longest common subsequence in two strings. Based on: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Longest_common_subsequence_problem http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/Algorithm_implementation/Strings/Longest_common_subsequence
